Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.98,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Phải đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.59,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Gì đây?
